com.lukeleber.scandroid.gui.fragments.detail

Class ServiceFacetWrapper<T extends java.io.Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lukeleber.scandroid.gui.fragments.detail.ServiceFacetWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The data type associated with the current value of the wrapped ServiceFacet
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ServiceFacetWrapper<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PIDWrapper

    public abstract class ServiceFacetWrapper<T extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ServiceFacetWrapper<T>>, android.os.Parcelable, java.io.Serializable
    A common base class for all classes that act to wrap the ServiceFacet for use in a GUI. Generally speaking, all concrete implementations of this class will usually be found within list views and as such this class provides methods to make use of the view holder pattern.
    See Also:
